<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1329168-i-m-reading-the-book-of-illusions-and-i-am">I&#39;m reading The Book of Illusions and I am sure I will finish it but I am trying to decide if it is worth my time to read any of Paul Auster&#39;s other books. Can anyone tell me anything about this book in comparison to his others, particularly the ones that were/are on the 1001 list of books to read before you die?

Thanks!!</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1329168'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F50618.The_Book_of_Illusions">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1329168-i-m-reading-the-book-of-illusions-and-i-am">3 years ago</a>
